      "gemini_text": "With the purchase of our new building at 609 F St., at a cost of $32,000, and with the alterations necessary to adapt it to the needs of our business, we have greatly improved our facilities for transacting a general banking business, and we cordially invite the public to give us a larger share of their patronage and support.",
